timeline.bodyText:
If you're moving this to a new line, change the at = @At to new line, so like:
@Redirect(method = "doBlockCollisions,
    at = @At(value = "INVOKE",
        target = "Lnet/n...."
    )
)
This way it's clearer, at least it's the format I'm trying to migrate the codebase to.

